    "name": "Non Lea, Licking to save the world",
    "cat": "game",
    "subcat": "platformer",
    "desc": "What if you are the guy who has Heatstroke ,having only 2 minutes to live, but he imagine that he is hero who needs to lick citizens to safe them from the heat before he dies ?\n\nControls:\n\nMovement : hold click , to summon your tongue ,then rotate your mouse to move around the city (if you found rocks or garbage, hold and move your mouse backward)\nLick mode : press F\n\nRefill water : press E + hold your mouse on water machines/water pillar",
